2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2728,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/01\/prophet-jokes-truth\/","url_meta":{"origin":8233,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Joking: The Prophet tells jokes, but only in truth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, do you joke with us?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, I do not say anything but the truth.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1990 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2924,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/18\/excessive-praising-people\/","url_meta":{"origin":8233,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Humility: Beware of excessively praising people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: A man praised another man in the presence of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cWoe to you! You have cut your companion's neck! You have cut your companion's neck! If one of you inevitably praises his companion, let him say: I\u2026","rel":"","